definition:
Someone descended from Shimei who was A man of the tribe of Levi living at the time of Egypt and Wilderness, first mentioned at Exo.6.17; 
 son of: Gershon (H1648); 
 brother of: Libni (H3845G); 
 father of: Jahath (H3189I), Zizah (H2126), Jeush (H3266J) and Beriah (H1283J)
Group of shim.i (שִׁמְעִי "Shimei" H8096) 
 § Shimites, of Shimei "renowned"
 descendants of Shimei or Shimi
